1
00:01:26,439 --> 00:01:28,560
Jiang Yue said he would display my works.

2
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:30,120
Where are they?

3
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:38,519
Mr. Xiaojiang,

4
00:01:41,439 --> 00:01:42,480
you're here in person.

5
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,799
Are you still worried about me?

6
00:01:46,159 --> 00:01:46,719
Or

7
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:47,599
you want to search me?

8
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,480
If you want to see the painting, just look.

9
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,200
Don't play tricks.

10
00:02:01,239 --> 00:02:01,560
Lu Qi,

11
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:03,400
What are you looking for?

12
00:02:04,159 --> 00:02:04,719
Professor Chu,

13
00:02:05,599 --> 00:02:07,280
I'm just looking around.

14
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:11,240
Is this where Jiang Yue

15
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,759
promised to exhibit your work?

16
00:02:17,879 --> 00:02:18,840
I guessed it right.

17
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,039
Where did he exhibit it?

18
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,759
A small place is not good enough for you.

19
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:26,639
Or

20
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,599
he didn't even

21
00:02:28,599 --> 00:02:29,520
get you a small place?

22
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:34,639
No, Professor Chu.

23
00:02:35,039 --> 00:02:35,800
Jiang Yue...

24
00:02:35,879 --> 00:02:36,280
Lu Qi.

25
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:40,479
Mr. Müller is still waiting for you.

26
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,960
Jiang Yue will arrange it for me.

27
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:47,199
Jiang Yue has no say in 3Z.

28
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:49,560
He can only do

29
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,560
what his father told him to do.

30
00:02:53,479 --> 00:02:55,719
But I believe him.

31
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:56,960
You're still brainwashing yourself.

32
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,800
How can the 3Z Joint Exhibition

33
00:03:00,639 --> 00:03:02,439
be compared to Mr. Müller?

34
00:03:03,639 --> 00:03:04,439
Lu Qi,

35
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,120
you're not giving up on Müller,

36
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,400
but a chance to rise to the top.

37
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,639
Are you sure you want to do this?

38
00:03:16,879 --> 00:03:17,919
Let's go meet Mr. Müller.

39
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,960
This piece is so beautiful!

40
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:26,120
Who created this?

41
00:03:26,439 --> 00:03:27,000
Come and see!

42
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:34,919
Look!

43
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,879
It seems to have taken away my soul.

44
00:03:38,319 --> 00:03:40,000
This is the true dark imagery style.

45
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:41,120
Who is the author?

46
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:42,120
Lu Qi.

47
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,919
The author should be here, right?

48
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,319
Look, Lu Qi.

49
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,479
Miss Lu Qi,

50
00:03:48,479 --> 00:03:50,680
are you the author of this "Tearing"?

51
00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:51,240
Miss Lu Qi,

52
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,520
what inspired you

53
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,240
to create this work?

54
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:54,080
Miss Lu,

55
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,879
could you tell us about dark imagery?

56
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:57,759
What do you want to express in this work?

57
00:03:58,039 --> 00:04:00,360
Jiang Yue really showed her this work.

58
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,759
But if this could make her give up on Müller,

59
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,240
I absolutely don't believe it.

60
00:04:09,199 --> 00:04:10,120
Shen Yu, take her away.

61
00:04:11,319 --> 00:04:11,800
Sir, please go.

62
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:08,839
Qi Qi, Qi Qi.

63
00:05:10,199 --> 00:05:11,079
Miss is worried about you.

64
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,000
I couldn't stop her.

65
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,680
Sir, you can't go in.

66
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:37,639
It will affect the treatment.

67
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:05,839
Do you want to smoke?

68
00:06:06,839 --> 00:06:07,279
Get out!

69
00:06:17,519 --> 00:06:18,360
How about drinking?

70
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:22,160
What do you want to drink? I'll buy it.

71
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:30,959
Jiang Yue,

72
00:06:33,199 --> 00:06:34,480
don't you think you are tired?

73
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:38,759
Life is short,

74
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,839
why do you have to make the whole world

75
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:42,879
your enemy?

76
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,319
There are few people who can catch my eye.

77
00:06:54,279 --> 00:06:55,560
You are the most interesting one.

78
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:58,879
I want to be friends with you.

79
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:01,759
I don't want.

80
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,480
I want you to get out.

81
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:09,800
You know

82
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,079
the gun that made Lu Qi go to hospital

83
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:14,399
was not me.

84
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:31,959
Jiang Yue

85
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:35,800
Between you and me,

86
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,160
there will be a day

87
00:07:39,279 --> 00:07:40,000
to drink together?

88
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,040
Sir,

89
00:08:02,319 --> 00:08:02,759
the artists

90
00:08:02,759 --> 00:08:03,879
have arrived at the hotel safely.

91
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:04,879
The emergency plan

92
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,079
has been fully activated.

93
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:08,839
Where is Jiang Yue?

94
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:11,959
Master,

95
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:13,959
he is with Miss in the hospital.

96
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,279
Jiang Yue is the sword I cultivated.

97
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:24,120
I won't let Lu Qi take him away.

98
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,919
3Z wanted to use this to rise to a new level

99
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,240
and monopolize the entire industry.

100
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,039
Now, look at this.

101
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,840
It's back to square one.

102
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,879
How much money does 3Z have to pay?

103
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,159
Lin Chuanye

104
00:08:46,279 --> 00:08:47,519
once had a painting

105
00:08:47,519 --> 00:08:49,080
that sold for a hundred million.

106
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,840
Losing money is a small matter.

107
00:08:51,279 --> 00:08:53,360
The key is that there's no guarantee of credibility.

108
00:08:53,639 --> 00:08:55,360
Who will dare to cooperate with them in the future?

109
00:08:59,039 --> 00:09:00,080
Those artists

110
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,559
will be taken over by Black Snow.

111
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,279
Taken over?

112
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:07,919
Aren't they going to monopolize the industry?

113
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:09,879
Now,

114
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:13,440
they're back to square one.

115
00:09:20,279 --> 00:09:22,399
Jiang Changfa,

116
00:09:23,639 --> 00:09:25,960
you've suppressed me for 16 years.

117
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:29,720
Finally, I've taken my revenge.

118
00:09:38,559 --> 00:09:39,200
Secretary Li,

119
00:09:40,879 --> 00:09:42,919
book me a ticket to Florensa immediately.

120
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:47,080
I'm gonna bring all these European celebrities back

121
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:50,799
to attend our year-end joint exhibition.

122
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,200
Be quick.

123
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:06,200
He didn't answer.

124
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:11,679
Butterfly.

125
00:10:12,559 --> 00:10:13,679
3Z has been badly damaged.

126
00:10:13,919 --> 00:10:14,600
You need to act quickly

127
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:16,120
to destroy 3Z completely.

128
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,720
The patient has a mild concussion.

129
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:29,080
The impact caused contraction of the blood vessels in the eye,

130
00:10:29,519 --> 00:10:30,240
reduced blood supply,

131
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,120
which may cause visual impairment.

132
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,080
She's a photographer.

133
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,360
Her eyes are very important to her.

134
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,279
I just said "may".

135
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:41,000
We'll have to wait until she wakes up.

136
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:42,759
Then go figure it out.

137
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:44,799
Okay.

138
00:11:24,639 --> 00:11:26,600
The company is in such a big trouble.

139
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:28,919
Yet you're still wasting time here.

140
00:11:29,519 --> 00:11:30,840
Lu Qi is your daughter too.

141
00:11:31,639 --> 00:11:32,840
You don't care about her at all.

142
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:34,039
Why should I care about her?

143
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:36,000
What if it was me lying here?
